form, while still being super user friendly out of the box. Like yes, hypothetically you can…","fields":{"date":"2022-01-08T02:35:50.953Z","slug":"/blog/organize-your-shopify-settings/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Organize Your Shopify Theme & Section Settings","subtitle":"","tags":["Shopify","E-Commerce"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#98b848","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/254bc/featuredImage.png","srcSet":"/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/c2a4a/featuredImage.png 167w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/fe850/featuredImage.png 334w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/254bc/featuredImage.png 667w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/6f72c/featuredImage.png 1334w","sizes":"(min-width: 667px) 667px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/bcba2/featuredImage.webp 167w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/fb036/featuredImage.webp 334w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/bbe13/featuredImage.webp 667w,\n/static/2c5b9d2015432d858a54c43ca43b1be3/994d2/featuredImage.webp 1334w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 667px) 667px, 100vw"}]},"width":667,"height":350}}}}},{"id":"a6459bb1-f9aa-5d13-9b4f-b9dc789b2665","excerpt":"Don't be a T-Shaped Developer Be a T H I C C Developer Instead!  What's A T-Shaped Developer? The idea of a T-Shaped Dev has been around…","fields":{"date":"2021-04-10T17:07:45.666Z","slug":"/blog/be-a-thicc-developer/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Be A T H I C C Developer","subtitle":"Why 'Wide or Deep' when you can 'Wide AND Deep'?","tags":["Newsletter","Career","Automation"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/a2d68234f68f69b3186a2966b8c78e89/7ca88/featuredImage.png","srcSet":"/static/a2d68234f68f69b3186a2966b8c78e89/fec80/featuredImage.png 156w,\n/static/a2d68234f68f69b3186a2966b8c78e89/eeb29/featuredImage.png 311w,\n/static/a2d68234f68f69b3186a2966b8c78e89/7ca88/featuredImage.png 622w,\n/static/a2d68234f68f69b3186a2966b8c78e89/e696c/featuredImage.png 1244w","sizes":"(min-width: 622px) 622px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/a2d68234f68f69b3186a2966b8c78e89/ad4f0/featuredImage.webp 156w,\n/static/a2d68234f68f69b3186a2966b8c78e89/c740f/featuredImage.webp 311w,\n/static/a2d68234f68f69b3186a2966b8c78e89/9fde0/featuredImage.webp 622w,\n/static/a2d68234f68f69b3186a2966b8c78e89/0142e/featuredImage.webp 1244w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 622px) 622px, 100vw"}]},"width":622,"height":350}}}}}]}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","764694655"],"slicesMap":{}}